ARCHAEOLOGY: Study of past civilizations through their remains

Category: Science
Base skill: 20% (+5%/level, cap 98%)

Studying past civilizations through excavation, ruins, and artifacts.
On Rifts Earth this covers everything from pre-Cataclysm human
civilization to the scattered remains of far older, sometimes
inhuman, societies.

NOTES:
  No AetherMUD command currently rolls this skill directly. It is
  available for character concept and staff-adjudicated roleplay.

SEE ALSO: skills, anthropology, geology
